### Work IQ REST API — quick manual tests (VS Code REST Client extension)
###
### 1. Paste a delegated access token below (scope: api://workiq.svc.cloud.microsoft/WorkIQAgent.Ask).
###    You can grab one from `npm start` logs or from the Microsoft Entra token flow.
### 2. Run "Create conversation", copy the returned id into @conversationId.
### 3. Run the chat requests.

@base = https://workiq.svc.cloud.microsoft/rest
@token = PASTE_DELEGATED_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@conversationId = PASTE_CONVERSATION_ID_HERE

### Create a conversation
POST {{base}}/conversations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Send a chat message (synchronous)
POST {{base}}/conversations/{{conversationId}}/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": {
    "text": "What meeting do I have at 9 AM tomorrow morning?"
  },
  "locationHint": {
    "timeZone": "America/New_York"
  }
}

### Send a chat message with a SharePoint/OneDrive file as context
POST {{base}}/conversations/{{conversationId}}/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": {
    "text": "Summarize this document for me."
  },
  "locationHint": {
    "timeZone": "America/New_York"
  },
  "contextualResources": {
    "files": [
      {
        "uri": "https://contoso.sharepoint.com/sites/Engineering/Shared%20Documents/Specs/Business-Model.docx"
      }
    ]
  }
}

### Send a chat message with web search grounding turned off (single turn)
POST {{base}}/conversations/{{conversationId}}/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": {
    "text": "Summarize my recent emails about the Q3 launch."
  },
  "locationHint": {
    "timeZone": "America/New_York"
  },
  "contextualResources": {
    "webSearchOptions": {
      "isEnabled": false
    }
  }
}

### Send a chat message on the streamed endpoint
POST {{base}}/conversations/{{conversationId}}/chatOverStream
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "message": {
    "text": "What meeting do I have at 9 AM tomorrow morning?"
  },
  "locationHint": {
    "timeZone": "America/New_York"
  }
}
